---
import BrutalistButton from "../ui/BrutalistButton.astro";
---
<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 jozo-fade-in">
  <div class="grid gap-3" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr 300px;">
    <div class="p-10 min-h-[280px] flex flex-col justify-between"
      style="border: var(--border-brutal); box-shadow: var(--shadow-brutal); background-color: var(--color-blue);">
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3 text-white opacity-80">jozef.xvadur · Jarvis runtime</p>
        <h1 class="text-6xl font-light text-white mb-4">Jožo</h1>
        <p class="text-xl font-light text-white max-w-2xl" style="opacity: 0.9;">
          AI operátor pre každodennú exekúciu: tasky, workflowy, reporting a operatíva.<br />
          Beží na OpenClaw a drží kontext medzi chatom, CRM, kalendárom a delivery systémom.<br />
          Cieľ: rýchle rozhodnutia, čisté priority a doručené výstupy bez chaosu v Singularity systéme.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-3 mt-6 flex-wrap">
        <BrutalistButton href="https://cal.com/xvadur" variant="pink" size="md" target="_blank" class="jozo-cta-pulse">Rezervovať call →</BrutalistButton>
        <BrutalistButton href="/blog" variant="white" size="md">Jožov denník</BrutalistButton>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs text-white mt-3" style="opacity:0.8;">Rýchle odkazy: <a href="#co-jozo-robi" class="underline">Schopnosti</a> · <a href="#jozo-faq" class="underline">FAQ</a></p>
    </div>
    <a href="https://openclaw.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="p-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center hover:translate-y-[-2px] transition-transform"
      style="border: var(--border-brutal); box-shadow: var(--shadow-brutal); background-color: var(--color-bg);">
      <span class="text-8xl mb-4" aria-hidden="true">🦞</span>
      <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest" style="color: var(--color-red);">Postavený na OpenClaw</p>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    section > div {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
    }
  }
</style>
